WEBVTT

00:02:28.749 --> 00:02:31.729
yoriqlarnigina yopishi mumkin.
Materialshunos olimlar

00:02:31.729 --> 00:02:33.589
beton aralashmasiga
yashirin yelim

00:02:33.589 --> 00:02:35.649
qo'shib, yoriqlarni ikki baravar

00:02:35.649 --> 00:02:38.179
katta o'lchamda to'ldirish 
mumkinligini aniqladilar.

00:02:38.179 --> 00:02:40.069
Agar qorishmaga yopishqoq modda bilan

00:02:40.069 --> 00:02:41.559
to'ldirilgan tola va naychalar

00:02:41.559 --> 00:02:44.079
qo'shilsa, yoriqlar paydo bo'lganda,
ular yorilib,

00:02:44.079 --> 00:02:45.939
o'zidan teshiklarni to'ldiradigan

00:02:45.939 --> 00:02:47.509
yopishqoq modda
ajratib chiqaradi.

00:02:47.509 --> 00:02:49.469
Biroq, yopishqoq moddalar reaksiyasi

00:02:49.469 --> 00:02:50.969
betonnikidan farq qilib,

00:02:50.969 --> 00:02:52.709
vaqt o'tishi bilan yanada ko'proq

00:02:52.709 --> 00:02:55.209
yoriqlarga sabab bo'lishi mumkin.

00:02:55.209 --> 00:02:56.899
Ehtimol, katta yoriqlarni tuzatish-

00:02:56.899 --> 00:02:59.059
ning eng yaxshi yo'li 
betonga o'zini o'zi

00:02:59.059 --> 00:03:01.139
tiklashi uchun zarur
vositalarni berishdir.